'''''Excellent Sheep: The Miseducation of the American Elite and the Way to a Meaningful Life''''' is a 2015 book of social criticism on the role of elite colleges in American society written by [[William Deresiewicz]] and published by [[Free Press (publisher)|Free Press]].<ref name="official"/>

==Overview==
In his book, Deresiewicz addresses the pressure of succeeding under which students are put by their parents and by society, considering more particularly the ones that are planning to attend [[Ivy League]] universities.

